# 🚀 4) TRAINING SERVICE (AUTO-TRAIN)

## 📌 `training/train.py`

```python
import pandas as pd
import lightgbm as lgb
import pickle

def train():
    df = pd.read_csv("data.csv")   # ya DB se load

    X = df[["distance","rating","completion"]]
    y = df["accepted"]

    model = lgb.LGBMClassifier()
    model.fit(X, y)

    with open("/storage/model.pkl","wb") as f:
        pickle.dump(model, f)

    print("✅ Model Updated")
```

